Package agile.feature

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AgileObject
    The AgileObject class represents any entity in an agile planning environment.
    AgileSet<T extends AgileObject>
    A collection of AgileObjects that contains no duplicates.
    CapacityFeature
    Represents a feature that may be in or out of capacity.
    Feature
    The Feature class represents a subset of work in an agile planning environment.
    FeatureFactory  
    ProductFeature
    The ProductFeature class represents a TeamFeature that is capable of storing additional features.
    Program
    A Program represents a collection of ProgramFeaures.
    ProgramFeature
    The ProgramFeature class represents a feature that contains other features grouped by project.
    ProgramManager  
    Project
    Represents an AgileObject with current size and in-capacity size values.
    TeamFeature
    The TeamFeature class represents the final layer of decomposition of features.
